Class MultiDiskBTree

public class MultiDiskBTree
extends BTree

This class implements a BTree which stores its leaf-nodes on multiple disks.

Nested Class Summary
 class MultiDiskBTree.Level1IndexEntry
          This class describes the index entries for level 1 (i.e. the entries of the non-leaf nodes with level=1) of a MultiDiskBTree.
 class MultiDiskBTree.Level2IndexEntry
          This class describes the normal index entries (i.e. the entries of the non-leaf nodes with level>1) of a MultiDiskBTree.
 class MultiDiskBTree.Node
          Node is the class used to represent leaf- and non-leaf nodes of MultiDiskBTree.
